text: #BREAKING New Zealand's Cabinet has agreed to move to Level 2. Many businesses will resume from this Thursday, schools will open to all children from next Monday and bars can reopen from 21 May. #COVID19  https://t.co/AhL84ATOQd

entity.description: This page is a timeline of Tweets with information about the COVID-19 situation from the government, health authorities and other trusted sources across New Zealand. For more, visit https://covid19.govt.nz/.
